    <hr />
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>Our website puts small files called cookies on to your computer. </p>
    <p>Cookies collect information about how you browse the site. They can’t be used to identify you personally.</p>
    <p>We use them to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>measure how you use the site so we can update and improve it </li>
      <li>remember notifications you’ve seen so we don’t show them to you again</li>
    </ul>
    <p><a href="http://www.aboutcookies.org">Find out more about how to manage cookies</a>.</p>
